metadata.name: Officers of the 11th District of Amsterdam
metadata.description:
Original artwork is called "Officers and other civic guardsmen of the XIth District of Amsterdam, under the command of Captain Geurt Dircksz van Beuningen and Lieutenant Pieter Martensz Hoeffijser" (1613) by Jan Tengnagel. 

The artwork is combined with the Classical Doodles to have a twisted effect on what the original artist intended to convey to the viewer. 

5000*5000px
300dpi
